data.name: LebelEncodeHelp.Text
data.value:
To Encode your message, 1) Enter the message into the input box. (see image) 2) Set the Shift Number. 3) Click Encode. 4) Your very own message has now been encrypted. Only a person who has the encoded message AND the Shift Number can read your message.
**PLEASE NOTE: make sure that all letters which you input are lowercase.

data.name: LabelDecodeHelp.Text
data.value: To Decode your message, 1) Enter the message into the decode input box. (see image-right side) 2) Set the Shift Number. The Shift Number needs to be the one provided to you by the one who has encoded the message 3) Click Decode. 4) Your message has now been Decrypted.
